== Download gcloud sdk ==
* https://cloud.google.com/sdk/downloads#versioned

== Running gcloud ==
<pre>
$ gcloud auth list
$ gcloud auth login
$ gcloud compute instances list
$ gcloud compute ssh
$ gcloud compute ssh drewderivative@instance-1 --zone us-central1-a
</pre>

